Prioritize cache or warm_candidate for frontend, product-level, feature-level, UI, design, visual, customer-facing, dashboard, page, component, style, interaction, onboarding, checkout, editor, preview, review, or workflow changes.

Choose cache for likely UI/product work when dependency cache warming is useful but a full warm preview is not clearly justified.

